WEBVTT

00:09.481 --> 00:10.883
Chief Kent is here, sir.

00:12.199 --> 00:15.048
Well, let's have him, Baker.

00:15.049 --> 00:16.415
Thank you.

00:16.417 --> 00:17.515
Hey.

00:17.516 --> 00:18.746
Hey, hey.

00:18.748 --> 00:20.587
Man voted least popular
by the gangs of New York.

00:20.589 --> 00:22.527
(chuckles)
Thank you very much.

00:22.529 --> 00:23.594
Please.

00:23.596 --> 00:25.162
It's an honor.

00:25.164 --> 00:26.835
On the other hand,

00:26.837 --> 00:28.531
you're sending
so much business

00:28.533 --> 00:31.371
over to the DA's office
that they owe you

00:31.373 --> 00:33.338
a thank-you note
and a nice bottle.

00:33.340 --> 00:35.210
And every one is
a good collar.

00:35.212 --> 00:36.505
And by the book.

00:36.507 --> 00:39.912
Then they owe you
a case of nice bottles.

00:39.914 --> 00:42.542
I won't hold my breath.

00:42.544 --> 00:44.246
Seriously, Don,
great work.

00:44.248 --> 00:45.612
Incredible results.

00:45.614 --> 00:46.947
We're getting there.

00:46.949 --> 00:49.577
Briefing said
you're mopping up.

00:49.579 --> 00:50.946
As we speak.

00:50.948 --> 00:53.316
Well, then take a rest
on your laurels for a minute,

00:53.318 --> 00:54.758
starting now.

00:54.760 --> 00:56.623
I'm good.

00:58.034 --> 01:00.164
And how's Maggie?

01:02.072 --> 01:03.638
She's great.
(chuckles)

01:03.640 --> 01:06.447
Taking her out to lunch
today for our 30th.

01:07.281 --> 01:09.912
Congratulations
on that, too, then.

01:10.883 --> 01:12.554
Department should have
a medal for the wives

01:12.556 --> 01:13.692
that put up with us.

01:13.694 --> 01:15.959
I'll work on that.

01:15.961 --> 01:18.730
And let's book a date for
dinner, just the three of us.

01:18.732 --> 01:20.706
That sounds good.

01:20.708 --> 01:22.402
But you know Maggie will want
to bring along

01:22.404 --> 01:23.506
one of her girlfriends for you.

01:23.508 --> 01:25.979
What, she's still on about that?

01:25.981 --> 01:27.243
Same as it ever was.

01:27.245 --> 01:28.643
But you got my back, right?

01:28.645 --> 01:30.979
Until you say otherwise, boss.

01:37.790 --> 01:39.788
Little something
to wear at your lunch.

01:41.758 --> 01:43.164
What did you do?

01:49.540 --> 01:51.209
Wow.

01:51.211 --> 01:53.209
You earned it.

01:53.211 --> 01:55.544
Like father, like son.

01:55.546 --> 01:59.479
As of now, you are
officially a two-star chief.

02:00.481 --> 02:02.280
Don't know what to say, Frank.

02:02.282 --> 02:04.520
Then I'll say it for both of us.

02:04.522 --> 02:07.057
Thank you, Chief Kent.

